page.title: 06DIARY ENTRY: DOUNBY CHILD
page.content: I get up at half past eight and get ready for{school.}My school bus comes at ten past nine. We have playtime until half past nine then I go into class. We get swimming and I went in the deep end for the first time. We come back from swimming and get a playtime. We did a table square and saw a dead hedgehog. Then we go to dinner. We get out of school at four o' clock. I get home at twenty to five. I go home on the second run. I do some of my homework when I get home. Then I have some tea and go to {Brownies.}I was going to get a badge but it hadn't arrived. Then at eight when I get out I do the rest of my homework. Then I watch TV and go to bed.
